verbose_text: Fourth, the results of the present study demonstrated that Ang-(1-7) protected mitochondria against HG triggered loss of MMP, which was consistent with the findings of a previous study demonstrating that the Ang-(1-7) peptidomimetic AVE 0991 exerted protective effects in the kidneys in ApoE-knockout mice by partially reversing atherosclerosis related changes in the mitochondrial proteome.
